column4: Compact in size；Preset charging power & delay charging time；6A, 10A, 13A, 16A, 20A, 25A, 32A output current can be set according to grid type；Integrated RFID reader, supports whitelisting of RFID tags；Over current, over voltage, under voltage, surge, short circuit, ground fault, over temperature, leakage protections and sticking of relay detection；Wall mounted or pedestal installationt；LED status indication: power, connection, charging, malfunction
